Jim Rogers Sets Up Global Resource Fund With Citic Carbon, Post Reports

-- B y   S t a n l e y   J a m e s
-- 
2011-03-01T23:23:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-01/jim-rogers-sets-up-global-resource-fund-with-citic-carbon-post-reports.html
  Jim Rogers  has set up a new fund in
partnership with Citic Carbon Assets Management and  Banco Bilbao
Vizcaya Argentaria SA , the  South China Morning Post 
reported, citing Rogers.  The Rogers Global Resources Equity Index incorporates a
basket of companies with exposure to agriculture, metals,
mining and energy, including alternative energy markets, the
newspaper reported.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Stanley James at 
 sjames8@bloomberg.net  